{"tid":1445742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全世界同我死入黎，係香港人就入黎 好重要","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:24:46.000Z","uid":268373,"like":56,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0d3bb75ee8927af8bf17aea0b9c7e050b7255fa5","tid":1445742,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:28:33.000Z","msg":"屌你老母我愈睇愈撚嬲 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你老母死黑警又射頭又室內催淚彈又扮示威者捉手足</span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/izLdn3V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FizLdn3V.jpg&h=6921f34d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔缺前線，好缺勇武 我而家立即呼籲所有前線同我帶住一個勇武既心上前 佢地殺我地手足 視我地性命如無物</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我係呢到鄭重同你地講 有全何狗落單 唔理係咩品種 同我一堆人上去打佢老母臭閪 唔該你地諗返佢地點對我地 </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手足被害，十倍奉還<br />\n不撒不散，齊上齊落<br />\n行動升級，勇武對抗<br />\n唔可以輸，輸左我地乜都冇<br />\n背水一戰</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港、時代革命</span></span><br />\n大家唔洗驚，我呢個瘦弱學生哥會陪大家走落去<br />\n利申：發夢鳩up"},{"pid":"81860bb4bb711b1475cf2abbad3deaff5baf0907","tid":1445742,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:28:44.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"86086600e1cd15fcdc99fd6a6280e75ee3f4d5e5","tid":1445742,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:29:04.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"1c592ebbe60999c04d5616d44bc4529882ca294d","tid":1445742,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:29:17.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"37b28dea47431d6f1dd826c296612ffc0b3aa204","tid":1445742,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:29:37.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"336e45f4addc368d73bb192f398f90f629d26b06","tid":1445742,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:29:49.0